<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Hukdampa, gitloh meipi zing nuoi a hin,
 Lautha'n naubang ei puiin;
 Thisana Na tatsate gitloh a liemin,
 Nawpna luipi luong lai a chawl ie.

[V2]
 Nawpna luipi hung luong hen,
 Khawvel dahum a hin;
 Van Lal cha gilo Tanpa,
 Ka ma tieng pak thing bang lun zing hen.

[V3]
 2. Thil dang sangin, Na lopi zawi ka Hukdampa,
 Na thilsiem pakbang ka lawp;
 Thilsiem sangin Na hawihzaw ie ka Hukdampa,
 Na hehpihna mel ka gen thei puoi.

[V4]
 3. Lei hi Lalpa, Na thilthawn piek masa ahi,
 Ka sim seng puoi lei nawpna;
 Thangvan gamnuom Na vangsakna bukim ahi,
 Kalvari tangah kei nei pie ie.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Hukdampa!</title>
</song>